BASIC LEVEL:
    The page that returns the list of species available in the database is:  GET info/species:
        - Normal name: display_name
        - latin name: name (lo que queremos)
        - common name: common_name
    The page that returns the name of all the chromosomes of a specie is: GET info/assembly/:species
        - karyotype
    The page that returns the length of a chromosome indicated of a given specie is: GET info/assembly/:species
        - length

MEDIUM LEVEL:
http://rest.ensembl.org/xrefs/symbol/homo_sapiens/BRCA2?content-type=application/json